BEGIN_TEXT
Find the length of the arc formed by $BR
 \(x^2 = $a y^3 \) $BR
from point A to point B, where $BR
\( A = (0,0) \) and \( B = ($a2, $a) \) $BR
\{ans_rule(20)\}
END_TEXT

$newans = (8/(27*$a)) * ( (2.25*$a**2 +1)**1.5 - 1 ) ;
&ANS(std_num_cmp($newans));
